<h4>Data Notes</h4>
<p><a href="/about/fssa_m.asp">Learn more about the FSSA data &raquo;</a></p>
<ol>
<li>Prior to October 2003, IMPACT caseloads did not include Employed or 
Sanction clients. Beginning October 2003, ICES programming changes allowed the 
capturing of this data.</li>
<li>Child services data 
(substantiated and indicated child abuse and neglect data) -ĀA child may be 
counted more than one time and/or in more than one category. Therefore, this is 
a duplicate count. These numbers include institutional investigations.</li>
<li>Annual averages were created by IBRC using the monthly data and will differ from published reports that are based on a fiscal year. An annual average is not provided when there is no available data for a month in a given year.</li>
</ol>
<p class="source">Source: STATS Indiana, using Indiana Family and Social Services Administration data<br/>
